high_descs: Turn right walk forward then turn left and face the table on your left
Pick up the potato on the table
Turn left then head to the sink
Put the potato in the sink and rinse it
Pick up the potato in the sink then head to the microwave
Open the microwave and put in the potato
anns.task_desc: Put the clean potato in the microwave

high_descs: turn right and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the center of the kitchen island on your left
grab an egg off of the kitchen island countertop
turn around and walk to the wall ahead, then turn left and walk to the near end of the room, then another left and walk over to the kitchen sink at the end of the room on the left
place the egg inside the sink, rinse it off, then take it back out
turn right and walk over to the kitchen stove
place the egg inside the microwave above the kitchen stove
anns.task_desc: place a clean egg inside the microwave above the kitchen stove

high_descs: Pick up an egg from the table
Wash the egg in the sink
Place the egg in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg in a microwave
